metatags.og:description: Central Market/Plano HEB · At the beginning of my Culinarian experience,  I took a job as a dishwasher at the Manchester Hotel & Suites, from that period in my life, it has been my mission , to pursue the culinary skills needed to become a Chef in the profession that embodies the love I have for food and people. Every opportunity I have had, has given me the motivation that I needed to return to school and get a degree in the profession that I have dedicated my life to. Culinary Arts has been my  passion since high school. Each job that I have obtained has been the stepping stone that I needed to improve my skills as well as my work ethic. My  culinary education enhanced my desire to partake in the creation of uniquely savory &  seductive dishes that always leaves others intrigued. MATC's Culinary Arts Program gave me the expertise to perform in an industry setting, while absorbing the skills to operate my own Nonprofit agency geared toward educating the public on the importance of food security

metatags.og:description:
Culinary & Pastry · Hi! Thanks for reading this space!
I am a Chef with over 7 years of experience in Food Media and Food Industry. In 2010, at the age of 19, I entered MasterChef India season 1, with no formal training & made it to “Top 8”.I have also worked for/with Chef Sanjeev Kapoor, Maria Goretti, Kunal Kapoor to name a few. I am trained in Culinary as well as Pastry. I have successfully run a profitable Bakery during the COVID-19 pandemic. My background in psychology gives me an edge when it to comes to customer behaviour, understanding what they need & creating delicious food accordingly. I bring experience as well as cultural diversity to the table. Working in teams, in high-pressure environment with discipline and proficiency are habits inculcated over the years. The goal is to be a Michelin Star Chef; hence, I am looking for a full time job opportunity where i can train, as well as be an asset to the company. · Experience: Quail Valley · Education: BHMS Business & Hotel Manag
